  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Age ≥ 18 years&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Diagnosis of ischemic heart disease (diagnostic codes I20-I25)&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Referred for CR&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  HADS score ≥ 8 on depression and or anxiety&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Access to a computer or smart phone&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Ability to use computer or smart phone&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Proficient in the Danish language&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Signing an informed consent form&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Severe psychiatric disorder (i.e., borderline disorder, schizophrenia or bipolar&#xD;
             disorder)&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Severe cognitive difficulties (e.g. severe brain damage, mental retardation, or&#xD;
             dementia) that will prevent patients from participating&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Endorsement of suicidal ideation with daily suicidal thoughts (PHQ-9 item 9 &gt;2)&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Participation in other intervention studies (unless they are clinical studies)&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Seeing a psychologist or mental health professional for the treatment of anxiety and&#xD;
             depression&#xD;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
